value:
This outfit comes from Valla, one of
three places I call home. When I put it
on, I can feel the weight of its history.

Mutual caring and understanding is
what brings people together. That's
true no matter where you're from.

I wouldn't be where I am today if not
for the support of my friends. I want
to make them proud.

This Gullveig is said to bring ruin to
the future, but to me she just seems...
sad. I hope she finds a new path.

Askr is a mysterious place, isn't it?
Just standing here, I can feel its
power—almost like a Dragon Vein.

Thanks for coming out to greet me!
Here, I brought you a gift from your
friend $Nf.

War has taught me that strength and
conviction go hand in hand.
I will decide my fate!
I can't let everyone down like this...

I will use this power to protect those
who are precious to me.

I am Corrin. I come to this world with
thoughts of the people of Hoshido,
Nohr, and Valla held firm in my heart.

Even large-scale conflicts can be
caused by small misunderstandings
that spiraled out of control.$k$pI'm certain there are many battles
that could have been avoided if the
two sides understood each other.$k$pThat's why I try to see where my foes
are coming from whenever I can.$k$pEven if that's harder than a battle
would be, and even if it's likely we'll
fail to reconcile...it's worth the effort.$k$pCome what may, I want to be able to
say for certain that I did all I could
to bring people together.$k$pThat said, with your support, I feel
like my chances of finding peace are
better than ever. Thank you.
I won't accept defeat.
This is my path!
No doubt remains.
Believe in me!
Still not enough?
What do you think of this outfit? Does it suit me?
*startle* Your hands are so cold! You need to warm up.
My greatest strength is my faith—and that my friends and allies are worthy of my faith.
I am certain now that the path I chose was correct.
The veiled kingdom is neither Hoshido nor Nohr. It's Valla.
I get the sense that I was somehow called here by many voices...
My wish is to remain by your side. I want to support you however I can.
Understood.
Oh?
I will not fear.
